[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Miss Hoa, your son has 5th degree burn on 40% of body due to working accident.[p]
He needs to change his bandage 2 to 3 times a day, every time it takes a few hours to do so. The injury makes his body lost the ability to balance temperature and very easy to catch a fever any time.[p]
He should have been sent to a personal room with 24/7 fireplace long ago but the family couldn't afford it. You know well enough that he needs more professional care from the nurse.[p]
I don't know what rumours you heard but this nurse right here has all the good grades from her time at school and my assist in any mistake that she can possibly make.[p]
I guarantee you this is the better option for the patient[p]
[_tb_end_text]

