The middle aged woman bites her lip, looking at her son covering in white bandage on the hospital bed.[p]
After Kai's signal, i go to the patient's bed, check his diagnose and start changing his bandages. The injuries still produce mucus and makes the guy scream in pain.[p]
I have to calm him down along with his mom and change the bandage as slowly and carefully as possible while Kai walks around, talking to other patients.[p]
The pain gets even worse when i disinfect his injuries. My hands grow numb after i finish everything, infuse medicines and check his temperature. The red mark from the slap earlier didn't help either[p]
[_tb_end_text]

